attributes.description: Process executions on macOS monitored by Google Santa.

params.markdown:
![Santa Icon](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/google/santa/main/Source/gui/Resources/Images.xcassets/AppIcon.appiconset/santa-hat-icon-128.png)  
Google Santa is a binary whitelisting/blacklisting system for macOS that monitors process executions.
